                            <p><strong>The Winter Skin Set</strong> offers a full regimen to target dull, dry and uneven skin texture with products that offer hydration and skin barrier support. Includes a complementary pouch to store the formulations for your daily regimen.</p>
<p>This set includes...</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Glycolipid Cream Cleanser</strong> is a gentle, non-stripping cleanser that removes makeup and impurities while respecting the skin barrier to maintain hydration.</li>
<li><strong>Saccharomyces Ferment 30% Milky Toner</strong> is a gentle exfoliating toner that gently exfoliates to encourage brighter, more radiant skin. It gives all-day hydration and smooths skin texture.</li>
<li><strong>Hyaluronic Acid 2% + B5</strong> is a lightweight hyaluronic acid serum that brings together five forms of hyaluronic acid to provide instant plumping hydration, while smoothing texture. The additional supporting ingredients of ceramides and pro-vitamin B5 help to restore the moisture barrier to keep hydration locked in.</li>
<li><strong>Natural Moisturizing Factors + HA</strong> is a daily moisturizer, suitable for all skin types, that strengthens the skin&rsquo;s barrier whilst providing immediate and all-day hydration.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>To use the formulations together in a regimen:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Prep:</strong> Cleanse morning and evening with Glycolipid Cream Cleanser. Follow with Saccharomyces Ferment 30% Milky Toner.</li>
<li><strong>Treat:</strong> After cleansing and toning, apply a few drops of Hyaluronic Acid 2% + B5</li>
<li><strong>Seal:</strong> Finish your regimen with a small amount of Natural Moisturizing Factors + HA.&nbsp;</li>
</ol>
